Millie Bobby Brown is a Keeping Up With the Kardashians superfan, okurrr?! During an appearance on The Tonight Show last night, the Stranger Things star revealed which binge-worthy TV show she’s obsessed with. ” Keeping Up With the Kardashians all the way. I love them,” the 13-year-old gushed….
